// Deferred (follow-up will append at === MORE DISTRIBUTIONS APPEND POINT ===):
//   binomial_distribution, negative_binomial_distribution, geometric_distribution
//   gamma_distribution, weibull_distribution, extreme_value_distribution
//   lognormal_distribution, chi_squared_distribution, cauchy_distribution
